<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="tagDoc" id="tagDesc_layer"><h2>&lt;layer&gt; layer</h2><h3>Description:</h3><p> An independent stream of events on a staff. The term 'layer' in used instead of 'voice'
      in order to avoid confusion between 'voice' and 'voice leading'. The n attribute is used
